        "timestamp": "2021-03-26 11:31:38.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review+1\n\nAddresses the issue with a badly configured empty RIC URL - causing log flooding with warnings.\n(Even with such warnings/exceptions the A1-PMS operates as expected)\nSuch mis-configurations should be expected. \nThis check works no matter where the configuration comes from (OOM, ConfigMap, REST config interface, Consul, application_configuration.yaml)\n\nOOM Honolulu has an issue with how RICs are configured in general - To be addressed separately in Istanbul\nThis fix will handle that mis-configuration gracefully.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
